This is the outline of the menu associated with the Camera.

We want 2 functionalities from this tool. 
Slow movement at a specific rate
Or we want No movement between multiple pictures (snap, move, snap, move, etc...).


* Panoramic
** Start
** Settings
*** Total Viewing Angle (From 0 to 360 in 5 degree increments)
*** Focal Length (from 10mm to 800mm)
*** Overlaping (in degrees)
* Tracking (requires bulb to be set on the camera)
** Start
** Settings
*** Speed (degrees/min)
* Options
** Right to Left
** Version